          "tocNumber": 0,
          "text": "<p id=\"3440\"><format class=\"hadith\" who=\"17\" Id=\"1361\" RevayatIndex=\"1378\">وَ عَلَى اَلثَّالِثَةِ‌: <format class=\"ayah\" surah=\"48\" ayah=\"29\" toAyah=\"\">(فَاسْتَغْلَظَ فَاسْتَوىٰ عَلىٰ سُوقِهِ يُعْجِبُ اَلزُّرّٰاعَ‌)<format class=\"ayahWord\" fromWord=\"39\" toWord=\"44\"/><format class=\"ayahAddress\" surah=\"48\" ayah=\"29\" toAyah=\"\"/></format>.</format></p>"
        },
